Package: lavaanMediation
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Parallel Mediation Analysis with 'lavaan'
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Congqing", "He",
      email = "hecongqing@hotmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a Shiny interface for fitting and exploring parallel
    mediation models with 'lavaan'. The application supports multiple
    mediators, optional covariates, bootstrap confidence intervals for
    indirect effects, model-fit summaries, parameter tables, path diagrams,
    and downloadable results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    htmltools (>= 0.5.7),
    lavaan (>= 0.6-15),
    semPlot (>= 1.1.6),
    shiny (>= 1.7.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/hecongqing/lavaanMediation
BugReports: https://github.com/hecongqing/lavaanMediation/issues
